                    "question": "<div style='text-align: justify;'>An electric bulb is rated 220 V and 100 W. When it is operated on 110 V, the power consumed will be _____.<br/>(a) 100 W<br/>(b) 75 W<br/>(c) 50 W<br/>(d) 25 W</div>",
