                        "<div style='text-align: justify;'><b>Parallel:</b> R<sub>p</sub> = R/2. Heat produced H<sub>p</sub> = V<sup>2</sup>t / (R/2) = 2V<sup>2</sup>t / R.</div>",
                        "<div style='text-align: justify;'>Ratio H<sub>s</sub>/H<sub>p</sub> = (V<sup>2</sup>t / 2R) / (2V<sup>2</sup>t / R) = 1/4.</div>",
                        "<div style='text-align: justify;'>Thus, the correct option is <b>(o)</b>.</div>",
