                        "<div style='text-align: justify;'>Area (A) = &pi;d<sup>2</sup>/4 = 3.14 &times; (5 &times; 10<sup>-4</sup>)<sup>2</sup> / 4 &approx; 1.96 &times; 10<sup>-7</sup> m<sup>2</sup>.</div>",
